WHY   — It is the machine taught to edit itself: shown its own worst answer, asked what's wrong with it, and made to write the better one — self-correction as a training signal.
HOW   — Folded in from Anthropic's public git (paper arXiv:2212.08073 + repos), cited not claimed, no data shipped.

